headline: Retail Strength Balances Softer Discretionary Sales, According to October Fiserv Small Business Index
summary: MILWAUKEE, November 03, 2025--Fiserv, Inc. (NYSE: FI), a leading global provider of payments and financial services technology, has published the Fiserv Small Business Index for October 2025, with the seasonally adjusted Index holding steady at 148.

headline: This Week In Digital Payment - Singapore's Financial Ecosystem Transformation Through Innovation
